<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The Council and the People honoured with the finest and greatest honours Molossos son of Peritas the son of Artemidoros Grypos, ?when he became priest of Hermes Agoraios, while a child in age.</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>The use of <foreign lang="grc">γενόμενον</foreign> in line 5 suggest that these honours were decreed at the time that Molossos became a priest.</p>
</div>
